Слайдер (Карусель)
Слайдер или карусель в Materialize CSS позволяет создавать слайд-шоу изображений. Вот пример, как создать и инициализировать слайдер:

Copy
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Slider Example</title>
    <!-- Подключение Materialize CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Slider -->
    <div class="slider">
        <ul class="slides">
            <li>
                <img src="https://loremflickr.com/580/250/dog" alt="Slide 1">
                <div class="caption center-align">
                    <h3>Slide 1</h3>
                    <h5 class="light grey-text text-lighten-3">Description for slide 1.</h5>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="https://loremflickr.com/580/250/cat" alt="Slide 2">
                <div class="caption left-align">
                    <h3>Slide 2</h3>
                    <h5 class="light grey-text text-lighten-3">Description for slide 2.</h5>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="https://loremflickr.com/580/250/paris" alt="Slide 3">
                <div class="caption right-align">
                    <h3>Slide 3</h3>
                    <h5 class="light grey-text text-lighten-3">Description for slide 3.</h5>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Подключение jQuery и Materialize JS -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/js/materialize.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Инициализация Slider -->
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $('.slider').slider();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
